      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle at a great value? This car is in honest, fair condition and is ready to keep on rolling! It shows some expected wear and tear from its years on the road, but it remains a functional and reliable choice for anyone looking for practical transportation. Come see the character this car has to offer!",
