    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and will require a professional mechanical overhaul to be reliably roadworthy. Visually, the body shows significant signs of age, including bubbling rust on the door panels and several noticeable scrapes. The interior upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing on the rear bench, and the air conditioning is non-functional.",
