    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring consistent performance and a sophisticated presence on the road. Featuring a comprehensive service history and a well-appointed interior, it offers a balanced proposition of luxury and dependability. We invite discerning buyers to experience a vehicle that stands as a testament to diligent ownership and enduring quality.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
