      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s super comfortable for those long weekend trips or just zipping around town. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new owner to take it on some fresh adventures. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-strung power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been recently serviced to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has undergone critical subframe reinforcement, mitigating the common fatigue issues associated with the E46 platform. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-variable differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit stability. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the car's celebrated handling dynamics. This example represents a solid, driver-oriented machine with all major preventative maintenance addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Well-maintained vehicle. Runs smooth. Clean interior. Minimal cosmetic wear. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with elegance. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous finish, and while a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only light natural creasing on the driver's bolster. Mechanically, the car is in top form, having received regular synthetic oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. All onboard technology, including the navigation system and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. With a fresh set of tires and recent brake service, this car is ready for the road with no immediate work required. It is an honest, reliable, and thoroughly enjoyable vehicle for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this meticulously maintained vehicle offers a seamless blend of performance and sophistication. Exhibiting a well-preserved exterior and a refined interior cabin, the vehicle has been subjected to rigorous standards of upkeep to ensure continued mechanical reliability. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning individual seeking a high-caliber driving experience at an exceptional value. We invite you to inspect this exemplary specimen, which stands as a testament to conscientious ownership and enduring quality.",
      "price": 34900.0,
